WEBVTT

02:00.560 --> 02:03.280
Luo Wei grew up in the old town.

02:03.360 --> 02:04.920
She's probably not Xiaowei.

02:05.720 --> 02:07.720
But after she left the old town,

02:07.800 --> 02:10.039
no one has ever seen Luo Wei again.

02:16.440 --> 02:20.200
Maybe… Xiaowei has taken her form.

02:20.920 --> 02:24.200
The real Luo Wei might have died long ago.

02:24.800 --> 02:26.240
Xiaowei's a thousand-year fox demon.

02:26.320 --> 02:29.320
Killing Wei Qing would be easy for her.

02:29.920 --> 02:31.320
She wouldn't need poison.

02:32.560 --> 02:37.120
Maybe… she's trying to frame someone?

02:37.200 --> 02:40.600
Or perhaps, for some reason,

02:45.040 --> 02:46.920
she's hesitating to use her magic.

02:52.440 --> 02:54.400
You scared me!

03:01.120 --> 03:03.320
You have Xiaowei's broken tail, right?

03:03.400 --> 03:04.680
Can't you track her?

03:05.720 --> 03:08.480
Only when she uses demon magic
can the tail sense her.

03:08.560 --> 03:12.280
But unless she's desperate,
she won't use her magic.

03:13.880 --> 03:14.720
Why?

03:15.320 --> 03:19.680
Because once she uses it,
the Ice Curse will come after her.

03:21.920 --> 03:23.440
Ice Curse?

03:24.680 --> 03:26.720
Xiaowei once fell in love,

03:26.800 --> 03:30.320
ate human hearts, and her crimes
triggered the punishment.

03:30.960 --> 03:33.920
So now, the Ice Curse chases her forever.

03:34.960 --> 03:38.280
That's why she cut off her spiritual tail
to hide her demonic energy.

03:41.320 --> 03:42.480
Spiritual tail?

03:43.840 --> 03:45.600
Of the nine-tailed fox's nine tails,

03:45.680 --> 03:48.360
the most important one
is the spiritual tail.

03:48.440 --> 03:51.040
It's also tied to one of the five senses.

03:52.200 --> 03:53.760
Xiaowei's spiritual tail

03:54.320 --> 03:56.120
is linked to her sense of smell.

03:57.360 --> 04:00.240
But last night,
the Ice Curse still appeared.

04:06.960 --> 04:11.360
That means she used her magic last night.

04:15.640 --> 04:17.000
GOLDEN WEAVE

04:17.079 --> 04:18.200
Luo Wei!

04:19.000 --> 04:21.240
How dare you poison me!

04:21.320 --> 04:23.800
Get out of the Wei mansion right now!

04:26.080 --> 04:28.600
I just couldn't bear
to see you marry another.

04:29.320 --> 04:31.480
So I wanted you
to fall ill before the wedding

04:31.560 --> 04:32.800
and call it off.

04:33.920 --> 04:35.480
I prepared an antidote.

04:36.080 --> 04:37.920
I never meant to hurt you.

04:38.000 --> 04:40.720
Wei Qing. Wei Qing…

04:41.600 --> 04:42.720
Wei Qing…

05:36.120 --> 05:37.120
Yu…

05:38.760 --> 05:39.880
Yu!

05:41.480 --> 05:43.080
Oh no!

05:44.800 --> 05:47.160
I'm under a death curse! What do we do?

05:49.040 --> 05:50.320
Do you know what to do?

05:51.440 --> 05:52.440
You don't.

05:52.520 --> 05:55.560
Why aren't you saying anything?
You can't talk.

05:56.560 --> 05:57.560
Yu!

06:05.840 --> 06:06.800
Yu!

06:06.880 --> 06:08.760
Ms. Yu, your sachet!

06:09.920 --> 06:11.040
Yu!

06:20.960 --> 06:22.480
The Wei family is really lively.

06:23.120 --> 06:24.800
There's a good show every day.

06:25.480 --> 06:27.000
Shengwei…

06:29.360 --> 06:31.720
SHENGWEI

06:33.600 --> 06:34.640
Let go of me!

06:36.160 --> 06:37.760
I'm packing up and going back
to my parents' today.

06:38.360 --> 06:39.560
Are you crazy?

06:39.640 --> 06:42.520
We just got married,
and now you want to leave?

06:42.600 --> 06:45.160
Do you want me to become
the laughingstock of all Luo'an city?

06:45.240 --> 06:46.200
Wei Qing,

06:46.280 --> 06:49.120
when I saw you and Steward Luo
holding each other just now,

06:49.200 --> 06:50.320
I woke up.

06:52.360 --> 06:54.840
What I felt for you
was just a fleeting crush,

06:56.360 --> 06:57.480
not real love.

06:57.560 --> 07:00.600
You married into this family,
so you belong to the Weis now.

07:00.680 --> 07:02.120
You don't have to love me,

07:02.200 --> 07:04.680
but you can't bring shame to this family.

07:04.760 --> 07:08.800
If you want to leave,
you'll have to be carried out dead!

07:11.200 --> 07:13.000
How did you become like this?

07:14.400 --> 07:17.880
I was so blind back then!

07:17.960 --> 07:19.080
Sorry!

07:22.960 --> 07:24.400
Am I interrupting?

07:24.480 --> 07:25.640
Ms. Yu,

07:25.720 --> 07:28.600
just now, you dropped your sachet.

07:45.200 --> 07:46.880
This is the token of love you gave me.

07:51.320 --> 07:52.480
Here, I'm returning it.

07:53.520 --> 07:56.440
From now on, we're even!

07:58.160 --> 07:59.240
Fine!

08:00.440 --> 08:02.200
You said it.

08:02.280 --> 08:03.800
We're done!

08:14.520 --> 08:15.720
What a mess.

08:31.280 --> 08:34.720
CLOUDS HIDE THE MOON, BUT NOT MY HEART

08:34.799 --> 08:38.159
THE SILENT STRUGGLE, NO WORDS CAN START

09:30.600 --> 09:31.760
Mr. Liu,

09:32.960 --> 09:34.400
looking for something?

09:36.400 --> 09:38.560
I heard my cousin
and his wife had a fight,

09:38.640 --> 09:40.440
and their love token got lost.

09:40.520 --> 09:42.080
So I came to help look for it.

09:43.640 --> 09:44.680
I don't get it.

09:45.960 --> 09:49.920
A couple fights and makes up in no time.

09:50.520 --> 09:52.760
Angry words can be taken back,

09:52.840 --> 09:56.400
but a lost love token is gone forever.

09:57.920 --> 10:01.160
What I don't get is you.

10:02.960 --> 10:03.840
What do you mean?

10:05.400 --> 10:10.280
Look, you secretly care for Steward Luo
and wish her happiness.

10:10.800 --> 10:12.800
So why not help her leave Wei Qing?

10:14.040 --> 10:15.680
But by looking for that token,

10:15.760 --> 10:19.360
it seems you want them to patch things up.

10:20.520 --> 10:21.640
Mr. Liu,

10:22.800 --> 10:26.640
who exactly are you trying to protect?

10:31.560 --> 10:33.680
My beloved, of course.

10:38.520 --> 10:42.640
Maybe I'm just a selfish man at heart

10:43.400 --> 10:47.160
who doesn't want to see her
in someone else's arms.

10:54.200 --> 10:58.000
Your hands are covered in tiny cuts.

10:58.640 --> 11:01.560
Looks like they were pricked
by something sharp.

11:02.920 --> 11:06.920
Were you cut by flower leaves

11:07.440 --> 11:09.080
while looking for the token?

11:09.160 --> 11:10.400
It's nothing.

11:11.160 --> 11:14.120
I've trained in martial arts
since childhood.

11:14.200 --> 11:17.240
Little scratches like this
are no big deal.

11:18.080 --> 11:21.080
Still, you should be careful.

11:24.160 --> 11:25.080
This way!

11:25.160 --> 11:26.360
Someone!

11:27.120 --> 11:28.200
You, search the east courtyard. Quick!

11:28.920 --> 11:30.000
-Hurry!
-Hurry!

11:30.960 --> 11:32.280
You, search the west courtyard!

11:33.600 --> 11:35.160
Quick! This way!

11:36.200 --> 11:37.200
This way…

11:37.800 --> 11:39.200
-Master Wei is missing!
-I'm coming.

11:39.280 --> 11:40.240
His life's at risk!

11:40.320 --> 11:41.720
What are you all dawdling for?

11:41.800 --> 11:43.440
Search, now! Search!

11:43.520 --> 11:44.400
Understood.

11:51.960 --> 11:57.400
Uh-oh. Master Wei,
mind being bait to lure Xiaowei out?

12:28.080 --> 12:29.640
Time for the show!

12:34.200 --> 12:37.960
All you demon hunters are just useless!

12:38.040 --> 12:41.080
A whole day's gone,
and my cousin's still not found!

12:46.520 --> 12:47.520
Can you smell the fragrance?

12:54.560 --> 12:55.800
The death curse is spreading further.

12:56.640 --> 12:58.680
It might've reached our sense of smell.

13:24.000 --> 13:26.400
<i>"See me in the afternoon</i>
<i>at the weaving workshop,</i>

13:26.480 --> 13:27.680
<i>and the deadlock will be solved."</i>

13:30.880 --> 13:32.160
Steward Luo,

13:32.680 --> 13:34.560
why did you go there yesterday?

13:45.680 --> 13:47.000
Where's Miss Yu Wei?

13:47.520 --> 13:49.400
She's missing too?

14:00.720 --> 14:03.360
Mr. Liu, I asked around.

14:03.440 --> 14:06.960
No one's seen you since last evening.

14:07.760 --> 14:11.720
May I ask, where were you last night?

14:12.720 --> 14:13.840
I was asleep.

14:14.440 --> 14:16.840
At dusk, my bedding got dirty,

14:16.920 --> 14:19.720
so I asked Steward Luo
to change it for a new set.

14:19.800 --> 14:21.080
She can vouch for me.

14:21.680 --> 14:24.960
Steward Luo, you even handle
little things like this?

14:26.440 --> 14:30.720
Mr. Liu's been pampered since childhood
and only sleeps on silk-satin bedding.

14:31.440 --> 14:34.120
Those beddings are locked
in the storeroom,

14:34.200 --> 14:35.280
and only I have the key.

14:37.480 --> 14:40.680
You all keep saying
this is the work of demons.

14:41.440 --> 14:42.880
So why question us mortals?

14:45.320 --> 14:46.280
You, Wu!

14:46.920 --> 14:50.520
Didn't you promise a barrier
to protect this household?

14:51.120 --> 14:52.720
All for show.

14:53.920 --> 14:56.760
The way I see it,
you're no folk demon hunters.

14:56.840 --> 14:59.360
-You're just frauds!
-I…

14:59.440 --> 15:03.360
Barriers only stop demons,
not the evil in men's hearts.

15:04.000 --> 15:07.520
Master Wei's disappearance
has nothing to do with demon magic.

15:22.120 --> 15:23.800
Someone used a spell in the workshop.

15:36.200 --> 15:37.840
The formation's been triggered!

16:13.440 --> 16:15.240
Hello there, Xiaowei.

16:49.200 --> 16:51.160
Thanks a lot!
This fox demon's no easy catch.

17:22.760 --> 17:24.560
Miss Yu Wei?

17:24.640 --> 17:25.960
How could it be her?

17:32.400 --> 17:33.880
Hard to accept?

17:35.600 --> 17:37.040
She is Xiaowei?

17:42.440 --> 17:44.400
I'll take her back for questioning!

17:45.080 --> 17:46.240
Li Jie!

17:49.560 --> 17:50.840
No.

17:51.360 --> 17:53.880
My sect has hunted Xiaowei for many years.

17:53.960 --> 17:55.120
I can't hand her over.

17:55.920 --> 17:57.480
That's true.

17:57.560 --> 18:00.040
However, the Xiaowei you're looking for

18:00.120 --> 18:02.320
is the eight-tailed fox
with one tail broken.

18:02.400 --> 18:04.080
Take a closer look at this one.

18:14.720 --> 18:16.920
Nine… Nine tails.

19:12.760 --> 19:13.760
Just as I thought.

19:18.280 --> 19:19.520
Help!

19:23.200 --> 19:24.440
Help!

19:39.280 --> 19:40.800
You said you never lie, huh?

19:46.160 --> 19:47.120
Trying to run?

20:08.920 --> 20:10.200
Miss Yu Wei, wake up!

21:21.960 --> 21:23.160
A double-flower hunter!

21:24.600 --> 21:25.880
Mo Yuntan!

22:08.600 --> 22:10.320
By heavenly law, return to source.

22:10.960 --> 22:12.120
Disperse!

22:16.880 --> 22:18.760
The double-flower hunter
is truly impressive.

23:30.560 --> 23:31.400
Wei Qing.

23:33.120 --> 23:35.320
I was so worried about you. Are you okay?

23:35.400 --> 23:36.360
Why are you all disheveled?

23:36.440 --> 23:37.440
Where's your belt?

23:38.160 --> 23:40.120
Steward Luo said
Master Wei's belt was broken,

23:40.200 --> 23:42.360
so she took it to mend.

23:49.200 --> 23:50.560
You are…?

23:51.840 --> 23:56.320
I'm Mo Yuntan, a demon hunter
from the Shilin Sect.

23:57.920 --> 24:00.440
A… double-flower hunter!

24:21.080 --> 24:24.000
With my binding seal, the blood of origin,

24:24.840 --> 24:26.120
all can be traced.

24:49.320 --> 24:50.560
Found them?

24:52.600 --> 24:56.360
But you said even if they fled
to the ends of the earth,

24:56.920 --> 24:58.760
as long as they're still in this world,

24:58.840 --> 25:01.880
your Blood Binding Seal
could definitely track them.

25:02.480 --> 25:04.680
They must have gone
to a place more distant

25:05.400 --> 25:07.440
than the ends of the earth.

25:08.280 --> 25:10.200
Is there such a place in the world?

25:10.280 --> 25:11.400
There is.

25:15.120 --> 25:16.360
The Formless Moon Palace.

25:21.360 --> 25:24.600
<i>Legend has it Nuwa</i>
<i>used spring water and clay</i>

25:25.160 --> 25:27.000
<i>to shape all beings.</i>

25:27.080 --> 25:29.720
<i>And since ancient times,</i>
<i>that water's been guarded</i>

25:29.800 --> 25:32.680
<i>by seven nine-tailed foxes</i>
<i>who are immortal.</i>

25:34.080 --> 25:38.600
<i>This sacred spring's location</i>
<i>is called the Formless Moon Palace.</i>

25:43.000 --> 25:46.840
Wangyan, we're back at the Sacred Spring.

25:47.960 --> 25:52.240
Why are you still nervous?

25:53.280 --> 25:55.960
Luckily tonight's the full moon,

25:56.640 --> 25:59.960
forcing us back by the Decree's power.

26:00.600 --> 26:04.440
Otherwise, that double-flower hunter
would've been hard to handle.

26:05.520 --> 26:08.240
I don't think he's that great.

26:09.640 --> 26:14.040
If my magic hadn't gone out of control,
he'd be no match for us.

26:14.640 --> 26:15.840
Don't underestimate him.

26:17.600 --> 26:18.760
Fine.

26:20.520 --> 26:21.880
Whatever you say.

26:27.840 --> 26:30.200
Let's start the memory sharing.

27:12.160 --> 27:13.320
<i>You're not Master Wei either.</i>

27:13.400 --> 27:15.960
<i>Master Wei wouldn't hold a knife to me.</i>

27:16.040 --> 27:17.800
<i>Such a beautiful vase,</i>
<i>and you have no taste for elegance.</i>

27:17.880 --> 27:19.360
<i>I know it's been a while…</i>

27:19.440 --> 27:21.280
-<i>Darling, why are you in such a hurry?</i>
-<i>Wu,</i>

27:21.360 --> 27:22.400
<i>my name is Ji Ling.</i>

27:22.480 --> 27:24.280
<i>Ji means "life's a journey",</i>
<i>and Ling means "hearts that beat as one".</i>

27:28.200 --> 27:29.440
WEI

27:31.000 --> 27:32.240
Disperse!

28:12.640 --> 28:13.920
Formless Moon Sect.

28:17.840 --> 28:19.800
I once read some fragments

28:19.880 --> 28:21.680
about ancient times
in the Dragon Deity's library.

28:22.280 --> 28:24.800
They say this sect, like the Dragon Deity,

28:24.880 --> 28:27.280
has existed since ancient times.

28:28.840 --> 28:31.720
It belongs to the nine-tailed fox clan,
appointed by Goddess Nuwa

28:31.800 --> 28:33.600
to wander the world,

28:33.680 --> 28:36.720
benefit all things, and uphold justice.

28:37.320 --> 28:41.200
They say this sect
reveals itself only to the fated,

28:41.280 --> 28:43.120
opens only to the summoned.

28:43.720 --> 28:46.320
Everything in this world can be traced,

28:46.400 --> 28:49.680
but that place alone leaves no trace.

28:50.560 --> 28:53.680
So Xiaowei betrayed her sect,

28:53.760 --> 28:55.960
and she's been hunted by the Ice Curse.

28:56.040 --> 28:57.640
Seems Wu Wangyan and Yu Wei

28:57.720 --> 29:00.520
were sent by this sect
to capture the traitor Xiaowei.

29:02.560 --> 29:05.800
Well, I have other tasks to handle.

29:06.600 --> 29:09.600
Everyone, please be extra careful.

29:25.040 --> 29:27.480
I didn't think Xiaowei would be so cruel,

29:28.400 --> 29:32.080
tricking me into the formation
to be her scapegoat.

29:36.240 --> 29:38.160
But when was I exposed?

29:39.440 --> 29:42.000
Did you use the Word Magic on anyone?

29:45.800 --> 29:49.080
I know it's been a while,
but you really don't recognize me?

29:49.680 --> 29:51.040
So she's Xiaowei.

29:54.160 --> 29:55.920
No wonder she's named Yu Shengwei.

29:56.600 --> 29:58.920
She can't let go of the character "Wei".

29:59.000 --> 30:00.800
Maybe it's not that simple.

30:01.440 --> 30:03.520
I used the Word Magic on her too.

30:04.560 --> 30:06.280
Quiet.

30:07.080 --> 30:09.800
Xiaowei's Word Magic is unmatched.

30:09.880 --> 30:13.760
If she were really Xiaowei,
I would've suffered backlash then.

30:17.920 --> 30:22.520
Maybe… the Yu Shengwei
we met then was real.

30:23.360 --> 30:24.640
You're…

30:25.320 --> 30:27.560
Rucui. Is it time yet?

30:28.280 --> 30:32.240
But the woman sneaking back later
might be a different one.

30:43.440 --> 30:44.520
Or maybe…

30:46.560 --> 30:49.240
when I used the Word Magic on Yu Shengwei,

30:50.840 --> 30:54.040
Xiaowei was also there, and she noticed.

30:55.120 --> 30:56.600
Oh, you're Yu Wei.

31:04.400 --> 31:05.520
That makes sense.

31:06.120 --> 31:11.440
Wei Qing, Luo Wei,
Yu Shengwei, Liu Weixue.

31:11.520 --> 31:13.480
It's a bit too coincidental, right?

31:13.560 --> 31:17.800
Everyone's name
has a word that sounds like "Wei".

31:31.800 --> 31:34.080
Thanks for saving me earlier.

31:34.160 --> 31:37.440
These past few days
must've drained your energy.

31:37.520 --> 31:38.560
Have some walnuts.

31:39.560 --> 31:41.120
It was nothing.

31:41.200 --> 31:43.120
No need to be so polite, Master Ji Ling.

31:43.200 --> 31:44.960
Yeah, no need.

31:45.520 --> 31:46.880
You didn't manage to save him, right?

31:47.760 --> 31:50.120
You almost got yourself caught instead.

31:50.200 --> 31:51.160
We're actually saved

31:51.240 --> 31:53.560
by Shilin Sect's double-flower hunter,
Mo Yuntan.

31:55.200 --> 31:57.040
Li Jie, stop it.

31:57.120 --> 31:58.800
Save him some face, will you?

32:10.360 --> 32:11.680
It's tasteless.

32:14.120 --> 32:17.440
Without my sense of taste,
I'd rather be dead!

32:20.720 --> 32:23.320
Well, that wish might come true soon.

32:24.960 --> 32:26.520
We've already lost three senses.

32:26.600 --> 32:28.120
In two more days,

32:28.200 --> 32:30.120
if we still haven't caught Xiaowei,

32:30.200 --> 32:33.440
the curse will consume us entirely.

33:06.120 --> 33:08.080
It's the dead of night!

33:08.160 --> 33:09.200
What are you up to?

33:09.280 --> 33:11.000
Do me a favor.

33:13.320 --> 33:15.280
Spit it out. What do you want me to steal?

33:17.560 --> 33:19.360
You know yourself well, huh?

33:22.680 --> 33:24.320
I need you to sneak into Weimiao Pavilion

33:24.400 --> 33:28.560
and steal those slips filled with secrets
from the donation box.

33:29.800 --> 33:32.120
The walls there are too high,
and a barrier's set.

33:32.200 --> 33:33.600
I can't get in.

33:35.120 --> 33:36.360
I've got it figured out.

33:36.880 --> 33:39.560
This mission is perfect for you.

33:41.040 --> 33:43.400
By the wall, there's a dog hole.

33:51.160 --> 33:52.200
Madame.

33:53.080 --> 33:53.960
Madame.

33:58.320 --> 34:00.240
-You may go.
-Yes.

34:03.040 --> 34:04.480
Such a big kite!

34:05.120 --> 34:07.360
Much has happened lately,
and the household's been unsettled.

34:07.440 --> 34:10.600
My husband got so scared,
he's been losing his spirit.

34:10.679 --> 34:12.480
Back in my hometown,

34:12.560 --> 34:14.760
they say when bad things happen,

34:14.840 --> 34:16.760
we can buy a kite and fly it away.

34:16.840 --> 34:20.360
The higher the kite flies,
the further the bad luck goes.

34:20.440 --> 34:22.760
So I picked the biggest one.

34:24.560 --> 34:28.560
A kite this size
must've been hard to find.

34:30.239 --> 34:31.280
Yeah.

34:32.360 --> 34:35.199
But I got lucky and actually found one.

34:36.199 --> 34:39.840
Maybe it was a blessing from above.

34:41.320 --> 34:44.480
Didn't she and Wei Qing fight
and talk about divorce earlier?

34:45.080 --> 34:48.639
They're back together so soon,
and she's so concerned about him?

34:49.800 --> 34:53.080
A couple just make up anytime.
Isn't that normal?

34:53.679 --> 34:54.760
You have experience?

34:55.560 --> 34:57.640
I… I really don't.

35:00.960 --> 35:02.000
Ms. Yu.

35:03.200 --> 35:04.080
Master Wu.

35:06.920 --> 35:12.320
Lately, you've been so dedicated
to hunting demons.

35:12.400 --> 35:13.840
You flatter me.

35:13.920 --> 35:15.320
It's my duty.

35:17.240 --> 35:21.160
What I meant was that smell on you…

35:21.240 --> 35:24.600
You haven't had time to bathe lately?

35:28.240 --> 35:29.600
Oh, I get it now.

35:30.760 --> 35:32.960
-This smell is…
-You're up early, guys!

35:35.920 --> 35:38.320
Master Wu, go wash up.

35:40.840 --> 35:42.520
You even smell it from that far?

35:43.760 --> 35:45.000
It really stinks.

35:46.520 --> 35:47.600
Come on, smell again.

35:49.280 --> 35:50.520
Just go bathe already!

35:51.640 --> 35:54.840
Fine, if you say so.

36:00.040 --> 36:01.560
You almost got me killed!

36:02.400 --> 36:04.320
Every night, they move that box
from the courtyard

36:04.400 --> 36:06.360
into Lady Wei's bedroom.

36:06.440 --> 36:08.080
Good thing I'm quick!

36:12.080 --> 36:15.640
But man, Lady Wei is really something.

36:15.720 --> 36:18.120
Her bed's all covered in silk-satin.

36:22.520 --> 36:23.760
So comfy!

36:29.320 --> 36:31.320
I nearly stayed there forever.

37:15.240 --> 37:18.480
Sister, are Mother and Father asleep?

37:18.560 --> 37:21.080
Why can't I wake them up?

37:22.280 --> 37:25.240
You're the child of a human and a demon.

37:26.920 --> 37:31.160
You can't cultivate normally
or control your wild nature.

37:32.200 --> 37:35.960
When you grow up,
you'll bring disaster to the world.

37:49.120 --> 37:50.560
Don't blame me.

38:12.760 --> 38:14.560
Are you a folk demon hunter?

38:17.640 --> 38:19.240
I'm from the Shilin Sect.

38:19.320 --> 38:22.600
There's a half-demon child here,
very dangerous.

38:25.520 --> 38:26.480
It's already gone.

38:30.240 --> 38:31.840
You did the right thing.

38:31.920 --> 38:33.520
Or when she grows up,

38:34.320 --> 38:37.800
she'll keep hurting those around her
and suffer herself.

38:42.240 --> 38:43.920
Why are you crying?

38:45.600 --> 38:46.800
Because the flowers…

38:49.760 --> 38:51.040
They withered.

38:53.680 --> 38:55.680
Though that joke's quite lame,

38:55.760 --> 38:57.760
I'll still laugh, I guess.

39:09.800 --> 39:11.240
Do you like flowers?

39:12.960 --> 39:13.960
Yes.

39:15.320 --> 39:17.640
Flowers just bloom and fade.

39:18.240 --> 39:19.880
No need to cry.

39:19.960 --> 39:22.960
In this world,
there's plenty to be upset about.

39:23.040 --> 39:26.720
Save your tears
for what truly makes you sad.

39:27.520 --> 39:31.560
If you have none left for those moments,
it will be even worse.

39:39.960 --> 39:41.880
I'm pretty sad right now.

39:49.960 --> 39:52.560
Let me take you somewhere.
You won't be sad there.

40:11.680 --> 40:12.840
Awake?

40:26.200 --> 40:27.840
Time to head back to the Wei mansion.

40:28.440 --> 40:31.640
We caused such a big scene last time.

40:31.720 --> 40:35.920
How do we face Wu Shiguang and Li Jie?

40:37.400 --> 40:39.040
We might end up fighting again.

40:40.520 --> 40:42.480
Why deliberately avoid mentioning Ji Ling?

40:46.520 --> 40:47.360
Him?

40:48.720 --> 40:49.720
He's easy to win over.

40:49.800 --> 40:52.040
Don't underestimate him.

40:52.120 --> 40:55.520
The words "fated one" are no joke.

40:56.920 --> 40:59.480
You're pretending
not to remember him, right?

41:05.000 --> 41:06.080
Wangyan…

41:06.160 --> 41:09.760
During the memory sharing earlier,
I saw it clearly.

41:13.160 --> 41:14.720
Besides you,

41:15.720 --> 41:20.280
Ji Ling is the second person
who truly made me happy.

41:22.080 --> 41:23.400
Just a tiny bit.

41:39.960 --> 41:41.800
So many secrets!

41:42.920 --> 41:45.200
Why are so many people praying for love?

41:45.840 --> 41:48.200
What's so great about love?

41:48.840 --> 41:49.880
Hah.

41:53.120 --> 41:54.040
How did you get these?

41:54.920 --> 41:56.800
It took me a lot of work.

41:58.120 --> 41:59.280
I'm so exhausted.

41:59.360 --> 42:01.120
Wu Shiguang, have you no shame?

42:04.880 --> 42:07.160
Why is Xiaowei collecting these secrets?

42:07.800 --> 42:09.720
It's probably her way of cultivating.

42:09.800 --> 42:12.080
Demons have many cultivation paths.

42:12.160 --> 42:15.520
Low-rank demons
suck the essence and blood of mortals.

42:15.600 --> 42:18.520
Higher-rank ones bathe
in the essence of the sun and moon.

42:18.600 --> 42:20.480
But Jiu Ying, the king of all demons,

42:20.560 --> 42:23.360
feeds on the hatred and fear of humans.

42:23.440 --> 42:26.520
The more suffering and chaos,
the stronger it becomes.

42:27.920 --> 42:30.560
The opposite is the Dragon Deity.

42:31.200 --> 42:33.760
People make wishes
and fulfill vows to him.

42:33.840 --> 42:35.960
He also gains more power

42:36.040 --> 42:39.920
from their offerings, worship, and love

42:40.720 --> 42:41.720
to bless all beings.

42:42.560 --> 42:43.760
And so it goes,

42:43.840 --> 42:47.160
justice and kindness in the world
keep growing more and more.

42:48.600 --> 42:49.800
Impressive.

42:52.920 --> 42:55.800
All beings have their secrets.

42:56.400 --> 42:58.280
Like love and hate,

42:58.360 --> 43:01.480
they are endless,
a resource without limit.

43:03.000 --> 43:05.480
This thousand-year fox demon
really is something.

43:05.560 --> 43:08.480
So, how do we find

43:10.240 --> 43:12.440
Luo Wei's secret?

43:20.720 --> 43:21.720
Look!

43:24.640 --> 43:28.240
"All merchants are sly.
That's how business works.

43:28.320 --> 43:29.480
By Wei Qing."

43:31.200 --> 43:33.120
Wei Qing also prayed for a love talisman?

43:35.360 --> 43:36.400
For Ms. Yu?

43:37.560 --> 43:40.840
No wonder. Forget love at first sight.

43:40.920 --> 43:43.160
It was all a setup.

43:43.240 --> 43:45.120
This talisman did the trick.

43:45.800 --> 43:47.120
Oh no! Ms. Yu's in danger!

43:55.560 --> 43:59.320
…CLOSE FRIEND. BY LUO WEI

44:09.880 --> 44:12.240
She tricked…

44:12.320 --> 44:13.720
Master Wei!

44:13.800 --> 44:15.160
-She tricked me.
-Master Wei!

44:16.520 --> 44:17.840
Master Wei!

44:29.240 --> 44:30.080
Yu!

44:30.160 --> 44:31.840
Ms. Yu, your sachet!

44:42.560 --> 44:44.720
Isn't it Ms. Yu's sachet?

44:44.800 --> 44:48.240
Wei Qing, Yu Shengwei…

45:07.680 --> 45:09.600
This talisman has two layers.

45:13.000 --> 45:16.040
YU SHENGWEI, WEI QING

45:20.560 --> 45:22.960
This isn't the one
Wei Qing got for Ms. Yu.

45:26.440 --> 45:28.400
This is Luo Wei's talisman.

45:29.440 --> 45:30.880
They were secretly swapped.

45:32.080 --> 45:34.960
He kept saying she tricked him.

45:36.000 --> 45:37.280
Who is that "she"?

45:37.880 --> 45:39.840
Only Xiaowei knows, I'm afraid.

45:41.680 --> 45:42.920
Not surprising.

45:43.000 --> 45:44.560
Fox demons are the best at lying.
